materials available in Clone Notes at
5&#162;/page.

<LI>Monday, August 19:
Uniform
 Resource Names: A Progress Report
<A href="http://www.dlib.org/magazine.html"><I>D-Lib Magazine</I></A>,
February 1996.
<LI>Monday, August 26:  <A HREF="#text">Text</A>:
  Chapters 
  <A HREF="http://www.december.com/works/wwwu/ch18.html">18</A>, 
